      "index": 0,
      "text": "Dr. Murad just reported that [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreKameaArano],Lady Kamea]] will recover fine, but she needs rest after that encounter with [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGrayNoton],Gray Noton]]. \n\nFor all it's worth I hope that I've convinced the doctor to stay with us, now that Kamea's [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAranoRoyalGuard],royal guards]] are leaving the company, since we can use Dr. Murad's medical and engineering expertise.",
