    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "59dbfa79623035dc22006847"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "God speed to all of them. I still don't agree with keeping Kamea on board as an [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAstech],astech]], even if she won't be piloting 'Mechs anymore in this company. \n\nAs long as she's on board this DropShip, we're at risk from the \n[[DM.Factions[faction_AuriganDirectorate],Directorate]]'s assassins and bounty hunters.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "I guess I'm a loyal dog. She was my liege in the Reach, and she needs help starting a new life.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 2,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "59b95c7d623035ac1400503a:5a7e395762303510120029cc"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
