    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "59b95f02623035ac1400505b"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "And about our financial situation? We need to raise more money so that we can pay our debt to the ATC as fast as possible and get out of this backyard. I can't wait to get to a place where most people shower daily.\n\nAnd if Noton learned Kamea's current location, then we can assume there are others with that information. We need to move as soon as possible.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 13,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "59b95c7d623035ac1400503a:5a7a243e6230351819000774"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3a06230355c18000067",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "5a7a24816230351819000777"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Sumire is right, if we keep moving that will make it harder for Kamea to be tracked and hunted.\n\nCommander {COMMANDER.LastName}, with your permission, I'll start looking for additional contracts, although we can't expect much out here. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Do it, Darius.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 14,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "59b95c7d623035ac1400503a:5a7a26e46230351819000899"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
