      "idRef": {
        "id": "59b95c7d623035ac1400503a:5a7a25ba62303518190007c3"
      },
      "index": 15,
      "text": "I just hope that we aren't carrying an albatross instead, considering how the past two years have been.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "The albatross only brought bad luck after the crew killed it, Yang.",
